                    <div class="card-title" style="margin-bottom:4px;">AI査定の将来予測</div>
                    <div class="forecast-value" id="forecastValue">176.8万円</div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="forecast-tag" id="forecastTag">6か月後 +7.4万円予測</div>
                </div>

                <div class="chart">
                  <div class="chart-line">
                    <div class="path">
                      <svg viewBox="0 0 300 80" preserveAspectRatio="none" aria-hidden="true">
                        <defs>
                          <linearGradient id="forecastGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="0%">
                            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ffbf78"></stop>
                            <stop offset="52%" stop-color="#f84ca2"></stop>
                            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#4db4ff"></stop>
                          </linearGradient>
                        </defs>
                        <path id="forecastPath" d="M12,58 C58,54 78,45 108,42 C142,38 174,40 206,28 C233,18 262,16 288,10"></path>
                      </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="point" style="left: 12px; top: 58px;"></div>
                    <div class="point" style="left: 108px; top: 42px;"></div>
                    <div class="point" style="left: 206px; top: 28px;"></div>
                    <div class="point" style="left: 288px; top: 10px;"></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="axis">
                  <span>現在</span>
                  <span>3か月後</span>
                  <span>6か月後</span>
                </div>
              </section>

              <div class="care-note mode-copy">
                <span class="mode-later-only">「まだ決めなくていい」を支える画面。出費管理があるから、アプリを消さずに残す理由になります。</span>
                <span class="mode-now-only">維持費が気になる時期こそ、価格予測が背中を押します。数字で見ると、判断がぶれにくくなります。</span>
              </div>

